    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 16 of the SLEEP program. The session works with what the difficult sleep years leave behind: the resentment, the self-criticism, the sense that your body let you down at a time when you needed it most.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how EFT tapping works",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Karate chop",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though those difficult nights still sting, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I've blamed my body and felt ashamed, I honour how hard that was.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though part of me is angry about the time I lost, I'm open to softening toward myself now.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tapping round",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Eyebrow:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I remember clock-watching and the dread at 3 a.m.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Side of eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I remember the heaviness the next day and the self-criticism.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I felt broken, like my body betrayed me.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under nose:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " Those memories still live in my nervous system.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Chin:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I don't want to carry the resentment anymore.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Collarbone:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " It only keeps the pattern alive.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under arm:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I can acknowledge the pain without living in it.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Top of head:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I choose to release the blame.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Reframe to positive",
            "type": "text"
          }
